    ..
 }



User <|-- Consumer
User <|-- Seller
User <|-- Admin

Consumer "0..*" --- "1..*" Product
(Consumer, Product) .. Comment

Consumer "*" --- "1" Product
(Consumer, Product) .. Rate

Consumer "1" --- "1" Seller
(Consumer, Seller) .. Rate

Product "*" --o "*" Category : Contains
Product "*" --- "1" Seller : Belongs

Order "*" --- "1" Consumer
Order "*" --- "1" Seller
Order "*" --- "*" Product

LineItem "*" --- "1" Basket
LineItem "*" --- "1" Product
Basket "1" --- "1" Consumer
@enduml

